9-02-25T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"爺你老母!<br />\n<br />\n雜維尼: 課左500億美金比TRUMP帝, 係香港部ATM禁返1000億!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:27:51.000Z","msg":"真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁搞法 港爆都未到支爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be7d2eea8aced675ae759ddb8d56d4e604ad235","tid":1036432,"uid":46814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"其實呢個前海香港鐵路2007已經開始講<br />\n連登仔後知後覺真係好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>根據深圳市規劃局在2007年7月編制的《深圳市軌道交通規劃》，該城際線屬遠期規劃，會在深圳西部的前海灣出發，經蛇口半島橫過深圳灣（香港稱後海灣）；進入香港後，在新界西北部分支，一支線通往香港國際機場，另一支線則連接香港商業中心區（即香港島中環一帶）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B8%AF%E6%B7%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8fY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=8ef8eaa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B8%AF%E6%B7%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF</a>"},{"pid":"a0260797302275765d36f0fa0e4dc18e35cee2a6","tid":1036432,"uid":130695,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"渣住本垃圾国護照就屌人要人認中国人<br />\n又要仆住搶其他國家護照<br />\n死磨爛磨 面皮無限厚<br />\n到班畜生拎到 即時又扮愛国 話做中国狗最好<br />\n要其他人繼續做隻中国狗要愛国<br />\n所以話中国支那賤畜蝗蟲真係幾撚恐怖<br />\n無人格無人性唯利是圖<br />\n玩個人崇拜 當個小熊維尼係皇帝<br />\n做哂太監宮女爭住奶<br />\n丫，我唔記得左<br />\n中国係最無骨氣既地方，打亂種<br />\n滿漢明清乜撚族都有<br />\n不過呢 都係中国狗，何必分那麼細"},{"pid":"833e6970056e1de24223643ca756890350f0bb43","tid":1036432,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4339f75c1de462ef59330d462e64cee0f476dfe3","tid":1036432,"uid":63154,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"佢當初想前海變另一個中環，變咗未？咁到底有冇美國啲金融機構進駐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計劃經濟一敗塗地，用咗七十年統治都未有一次成功過，知唔知醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"他表示，現時到前海一帶上班的港人，通常需要經由深圳灣口岸轉車，十分不便，因此有需要加建基礎設施，讓兩地居民可以互聯互通的。他笑言：「由於<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">現時人流不多</span></strong>，未能開辦全日巴士線...<br />\n<br />\n即係起鐵路蝕硬，真正目的係乜，大家明啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6f68563a844dd4297df8621848190b1aeaf5f5","tid":1036432,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"送禮黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564ed0fc25acda0f4765ac5208eb3f23ec9c2d7a","tid":1036432,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62a7e63fe2d3c9c0815e6c711d26a770aaf6744","tid":1036432,"uid":142359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebfca4d474eeb9b3baafc142441283d1c9d1c86","tid":1036432,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"到時又一地兩檢"},{"pid":"b587ea5ac3263e9f67c62fa7e72aa8edf4ec6594","tid":1036432,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"你以為新界d地係比原居民?<br />\n西北既地開始發展了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261fc4b7c668a324ce5932de99863d1a56cf2cbd","tid":1036432,"uid":11258,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"我都